Beyond grateful to have been chosen to work with some of my dream clients , so when I got the news that i would be shooting the print issue on newsstands to launch 2023 with @_noirmagazine , in this very special @TomFord cover, the only thing that could have made it even more of a blessing , was that @bymatallana was the one who’s creative vision would be lensing it. He has supported me since I was 16, and he is one of the most talented humans on the planet. & Thank you so much to the most extraordinary TALENTED team who shot this until 1am & made the shoot a dream. I adore you ALL SO MUCH. 🥹❤️
